  "slug": "cobblemon-pokenav",
  "title": "Cobblemon Pokenav",
  "description": "The Cobblenav mod is inspired by the item and related mechanics featured in the games Pokémon RSE and Pokémon ORAS",
  "body": "![Banner](https://i.imgur.com/zuMquLR.png)\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/Cobblenav/blob/main/LICENSE\"><img alt=\"GitHub License\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/gatekeep06/Cobblenav?style=for-the-badge&labelColor=black\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/Cobblenav\"><img alt=\"Static Badge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/repository-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&labelColor=black\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/Cobblenav/wiki\"><img alt=\"Static Badge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/wiki-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&labelColor=black\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gatekeep\"><img alt=\"Static Badge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/support%20me-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=ko-fi&labelColor=black\"></a>\n</center>\n\n# About mod\nThe Cobblenav mod is inspired by the item and related mechanics featured in the games Pokémon RSE and Pokémon ORAS. The mod adds a PokéNav that allows you to find out which Pokémon may appear in the area you are currently in, the chances of them appearing, and the factors that influence their appearance. The mod also allows you to track appearing Pokémon using a three-dimensional arrow or a radar item called PokéFinder. The mod is in active development, with new features added every month.\n\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"line\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m2OBcJj.png\">\n  <b><font size=6>Guides</font></b>\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Below are links to wiki pages where you can find information about crafting, commands, configuration, and add-on creation.\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/cobblenav/wiki/1.-Recipes\">\n    <img alt=\"recipes\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zGU6qw1.png\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/cobblenav/wiki/2.-Commands\">\n    <img alt=\"commands\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xE3IoSv.png\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/cobblenav/wiki/3.-Configuration\">\n    <img alt=\"configuration\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lJssyXW.png\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/cobblenav/wiki/4.-Add%E2%80%90on-Creation\">\n    <img alt=\"addons\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OZ4Z7Tu.png\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n<br>\nIf you are a developer, you may be interested in the <a href=\"https://github.com/gatekeep06/Cobblenav/wiki\">documentation for the API provided by the mod</a>.\n\n# Features\n\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"line\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m2OBcJj.png\">\n  <b><font size=6>Location Screen</font></b>\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  PokéNav will tell you which Pokémon can be spotted in your current location.\n  <br>\n  Accuracy guaranteed!\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"location\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/74I9DRg.png\">\n</center>\n\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"line\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m2OBcJj.png\">\n  <b><font size=6>Finder Screen</font></b>\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Find the best Pokémon in your area with PokéNav!\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"finder\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4HfT8SR.png\">\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>And track it down!</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"tracking\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y9iIKOx.png\">\n</center>\n\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"line\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LDOW4HM.png\">\n  <b><font size=6>FishingNav</font></b>\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Use FishingNav to predict your catch!\n  <br>\n  The mod provides a unique fishing spawn check feature.\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"fishing\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cvKVtqd.png\">\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"fishingnav\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/b9rXJB4.png\">\n</center>\n\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"line\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m2OBcJj.png\">\n  <b><font size=6>PokéFinder</font></b>\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  Do you find minimaps unfair or unaesthetic? Use PokéFinder!\n  <br>\n  With this small device, you will be able to access an easily configurable radar.\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"pokefinder\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JC9Uxb9.png\">\n</center>\n\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"line\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m2OBcJj.png\">\n  <b><font size=6>Add-on Compatibility</font></b>\n  <br>\n  <br>\n  The mod is compatible with all possible add-ons that use the Cobblemon built-in Pokémon spawn system. <br>Not sure where the legendary Mewtwo can be found? Leave it to PokéNav!\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n  <img alt=\"compatible\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OLf33cj.png\">\n</center>\n\n# My other mods\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobbleboom\">\n  <img width=160 height=160 alt=\"CobbleBoom\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VWlZyEe.png\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-let-me-spawn\">\n  <img width=160 height=160 alt=\"Cobblemon - Let Me Spawn\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VBgXD5r.png\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/neuromon\">\n  <img width=160 height=160 alt=\"Neuromon\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/71Kzdpa.png\">\n</a>",
